<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Armman <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt worden </del> / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l8">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd alſo hat vns 
<del rend="strikethrough">der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan></del> fricʒ derrer des p </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l10">
<add><ab facs="#facs_186_r1l1">hallers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_186_r1l2"><expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>Armman</expan> </ab></add> geſagt / daʒ <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_186_r2l9">ſeins </ab></add> yrchs vnd leders / cʒwelfhalbhundert </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l11">vnd cʒwelff 
<del rend="strikethrough">hie ve </del> fel / . ſein / in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> pellein vnd in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l13">korb / 
<del rend="strikethrough">dıe ſein / ſein / als </del>
