<del rend="strikethrough">das </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_186_line_1576739149595_383">
<del rend="strikethrough">die </del></ab></add> vor vns cʒu den <expan>heılige<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l16">behabt hat / daʒ die ſein ſein / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_186_line_1576739151974_388">vnd </ab></add> / daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_186_line_1576739154894_393">ſüſt </ab></add> / kein auſʒman <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
